<div class="home_page">
  <div class="container home-container">
    <div class="name">
      <h1>Pet Kingdom</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="us">
      <p>Whether you need in-home dog boarding, pet sitting, dog walking, or day care, Pet kingdom connects pet parents with people who’ll treat their pets like family.

      PET KINGDOM sitters are your rainy-day-pet-walkers, busy-weekend-pet-sitter and never-tired-cat-cuddller. Your every-day-belly-rubbers. Your tug-of-war players. Your middle-of-the-night-pee-breakers. Because we get it—your pet is family. And when you can’t be there, you can trust us to keep your dog happy, healthy, and sweet as ever.
      </p>
    </div>

    <% unless current_user.nil? %>
      <div class="btns_flex">
        <% if current_user.owner && current_user.sitter %>
          <%= link_to "Your Animals", animals_path, class: "dropbtn b" %>
          <%= link_to "Your Requests", requests_path, class: "dropbtn b"%>
          <%= link_to "All Sitters", sitters_path, class: "dropbtn b" %>
        <% elsif current_user.owner %>
          <%= link_to "Your Animals", animals_path, class: "dropbtn b" %>
          <%= link_to "Your Requests", requests_path, class: "dropbtn b" %>
          <%= link_to "All Sitters", sitters_path, class: "dropbtn b" %>
        <% elsif current_user.sitter %>
          <%= link_to "Your Requests", requests_path, class: "dropbtn" %>
          <%= link_to "Your Clients", animals_path, class: "dropbtn" %>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>

</div>
